Privacy Policy
Last Updated: September 2, 2024
Welcome to HEAVYPAINT, a service provided by HEAVYPOLY, Inc. ("Company," "we," "us," "our"). available as a mobile app on iOS and Android, and as a website / webapp at
www.HEAVYPAINT.com
.
INFORMATION WE COLLECT
We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when you register on HEAVYPAINT, express an interest in obtaining information about us or our products and services, when you participate in activities on HEAVYPAINT (such as by posting messages in our online forums or entering competitions, contests or giveaways) or otherwise when you contact us.
The personal information we collect is limited to what is necessary to provide our services and process payments. This may include:
Contact Information: We collect your name and email address to create and manage your account, communicate with you about our services, and process payments.
HOW WE USE YOUR INFORMATION
We use your personal information solely for the purpose of providing our services and processing payments. Specifically, we use your information to:
Create and manage your account
Communicate with you about our services
Process payments for services rendered
Improve and optimize our App performance and user experience across all platforms
Comply with legal obligations related to providing our services and processing payments
SHARING YOUR INFORMATION
We do not share your personal information with third parties, except in the following limited circumstances:
With your explicit consent
To comply with legal obligations
To process payments through secure payment processors
With app distribution platforms (e.g., Apple App Store, Google Play Store) in accordance with their respective standard policies, where applicable
We do not sell, rent, or otherwise share your personal information with third parties for their marketing or advertising purposes.
DATA COLLECTION TECHNOLOGIES
HEAVYPAINT uses cookies and similar technologies to help provide, protect, and improve the HEAVYPAINT Services. This policy explains how and why we use these technologies and the choices you have. This may include using local storage on your device to store preferences and improve app performance.
YOUR PRIVACY RIGHTS
You can review and change your personal information by logging into HEAVYPAINT and visiting your account profile page. You can also choose not to provide us with certain information, but that may result in you being unable to use certain features of our App because such information may be required in order for you to register as a user; purchase products or services; participate in a contest, promotion, survey, or sweepstakes; ask a question; or initiate other transactions.
DATA SECURITY
We aim to protect your personal information through a system of organizational and technical security measures designed to protect the security of any information we process.
UPDATES TO THIS POLICY
We may update this privacy policy from time to time. The updated version will be indicated by an updated "Last Updated" date and the updated version will be effective as soon as it is accessible.
PLATFORM-SPECIFIC PROVISIONS
For mobile app users: We comply with the respective app store's (e.g., Apple App Store, Google Play Store) review guidelines and privacy policies. Any data collected through platform-specific APIs will be treated in accordance with the platform's privacy standards.
For desktop app users: We adhere to standard desktop application privacy practices and any data collected will be handled in compliance with this privacy policy.
For webapp users: We follow standard web privacy practices, including the use of cookies and local storage as described in our Data Collection Technologies section.
If you have any questions about this privacy policy, you can contact us at
support@HEAVYPOLY.com
.
HEAVYPOLY, Inc.